00:42:02.500 --> 00:42:20.530
Raúl Kripalani: I just wanted to go back down here. So we've got, a million attesters, and the straw map says that… let me see where I put this… so the Straw Maps has this little box over here, which is 1208K attester cap. Why is that? Can…

