00:42:45.870 --> 00:43:07.179
Raúl Kripalani: Well, I think people are probably not able to answer now, because I'm sure that most of you know the answer. But the idea, the thing is that the network is sized in a particular way. We've got 4 seconds to propagate attestations, it is sized for 64 subnets, for the current volume of attestations, and so on.

312
00:43:07.180 --> 00:43:10.600
Raúl Kripalani: And the idea, if…

