00:43:19.180 --> 00:43:38.610
Raúl Kripalani: faster slots, and faster finality, right? So that means, or they're actually come together, they're stacked together. So this actually means, if you're kind of, like, naive, you can go and say, okay, if I… if I need to reduce my protocol, if I need to slash my timing in the protocol by, like, 8,

